				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/Kh%E1%BA%A9n-c%E1%BA%A7u/poem-BOjsbfHHkudHg7HGjezu5A">Khẩn cầu - 懇求</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-T%C3%B4ng-Phan/K%C3%BD-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-ph%C3%B3-Tr%C3%BAc-th%C3%A0nh-thi%E1%BA%BFt-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-DoKofZJSVgpP6sq_809o_w">Ký hữu nhân phó Trúc thành thiết trướng - 寄友人付竹城設帳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-T%C3%B4ng-Phan/author-fzCbnitCmoMjq_aSI076ow">Vũ Tông Phan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Phi/M%C3%A3n-giang-h%E1%BB%93ng-%C4%90%C4%83ng-Ho%C3%A0ng-H%E1%BA%A1c-l%C3%A2u-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-xyBW5ib-wf6u_UUj_3B_IA">Mãn giang hồng - Đăng Hoàng Hạc lâu hữu cảm - 滿江紅－登黃鶴樓有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Phi/author-c3LgePu9281GzRSNKjalQA">Nhạc Phi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/Nam-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-tCAQRSyZ99kw_BR4g9euCg">Nam vọng - 南望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-S%C3%B9ng-Ho%C3%A1n/Ng%E1%BB%A5c-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-YjlH0LItDtk3J4HpP-9Dsw">Ngục trung đối nguyệt - 獄中對月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-S%C3%B9ng-Ho%C3%A1n/author-khnDeiNFO_ApZONPmFuNuA">Viên Sùng Hoán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Quan-An-T%C3%A2y-binh-qu%C3%A1-ph%C3%B3-Quan-Trung-%C4%91%C3%A3i-m%E1%BB%87nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-i-r0uOp91u76yXFPCeZjKg">Quan An Tây binh quá phó Quan Trung đãi mệnh kỳ 1 - 觀安西兵過赴關中待命其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-m8buZGd9acbui1906QmgWA">Thanh Tâm tài nhân tập tự - 青心才人詩集序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/author-ZpBj6D9P3q-U3JR36g_w5g">Chu Mạnh Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-S%C3%A1i-Hy-L%E1%BB%97-%C4%91%C3%B4-u%C3%BD-ho%C3%A0n-L%C5%A9ng-H%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-k%C3%BD-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD/poem-84pNUNntDSUCkeWSBLVMWw">Tống Sái Hy Lỗ đô uý hoàn Lũng Hữu, nhân ký Cao tam thập ngũ thư ký - 送蔡希魯都尉還隴右因寄高三十五書記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-D%E1%BB%B1c-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/poem-TkW8fLOTmterjOmmEEwTBQ">Tương Dực đế - 襄翼帝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3i-T%E1%BA%A5n/X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-b%E1%BB%93/poem-5gNMScs-I4ipAv4Gl7gvuw">Xương bồ - 菖蒲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3i-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-bCxc2Eo5oW0L_EEb87EbHg">Giải Tấn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
